 <text>
  <front>
   <head>The SONG of SIMEON paraphrased.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="couplet">
     <l n="1" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">'TIS enough â€” the hour is come.</l>
     <l n="2" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Now within the silent tomb</l>
     <l n="3" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Let this mortal frame decay,</l>
     <l n="4" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Mingled with its kindred clay;</l>
     <l n="5" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Since thy mercies oft of old</l>
     <l n="6" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">By thy chosen seers foretold,</l>
     <l n="7" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Faithful now and stedfast prove,</l>
     <l n="8" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">God of truth and God of love!</l>
     <l n="9" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Since at length my aged eye</l>
     <l n="10" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Sees the day-spring from on high.</l>
     <l n="11" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Son of righteousness, to thee</l>
     <l n="12" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Lo! the nations bow the knee,</l>
     <l n="13" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">And the realms of distant kings</l>
     <l n="14" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Own the healing of thy wings.</l>
     <l n="15" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Those whom death had overspread</l>
     <l n="16" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">With his dark and dreary shade,</l>
     <l n="17" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Lift their eyes, and from afar</l>
     <l n="18" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Hail the light of Jacob's star;</l>
     <l n="19" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Waiting till the promis'd ray</l>
     <l n="20" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Turn their darkness into day.</l>
     <l n="21" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">See the beams intensely shed</l>
     <l n="22" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Shine o'er Sion's favour'd head.</l>
     <l n="23" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">Never may they hence remove,</l>
     <l n="24" met="+-|+-|+-|+" line_length="7">God of truth and God of love!</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
